rows.label: qst003203_msg0003
rows.name:
There is a Nopon girl named
Alulu-chan, mo. She fell from
Acedia with Bonono, mo.

rows.label: qst003203_msg0004
rows.name:
Bonono and Alulu were traveling
together, but got split up!

rows.label: qst003203_msg0005
rows.name:
Bonono is worried she was
attacked by those things too,
mo. Please help her as well, mo.

rows.label: qst003203_msg0006
rows.name:
We got separated, so I don't
know where she went, but I
think she went downwards, mo.

rows.label: qst003203_msg0007
rows.name:
Thank you, mo. She must be scared,
so please find her quickly, mo!
